com.microblink.image

Interface CurrentImageListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FrameCallback, android.os.Parcelable

    @WorkerThread
public interface CurrentImageListener
extends android.os.Parcelable, FrameCallback
    Callback that will be invoked when recognition process receives new frame for processing. Unlike FrameCallback, this one supports being transferred via Intent

    NOTE: After being de-parcelled, the instance of this interface's implementation lives in the context of activity that performed deparcelization - it is NOT the same instance as the original object that you sent.
